high_descs: Turn around and go to the left of the white table
Grab the knife off of the table
Cut the loaf of bread into slices
Look down at the table
Put the knife on the table
Look up at the table
Grab a slice of bread off of the table
Turn right and go to the fridge
Cool the bread in the fridge and then take it out
Turn around and go to the left of the white table
Put the bread on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting cooled sliced bread on the white table

high_descs: Turn around and move to the opposite corner of the room, facing the white table.
Pick up the knife closest to you off of the table.
Slice the bread on the table.
Face the table in front of you.
Set the knife back down in front of the bread on the table.
Face the table in front of you.
Pick up a slice of bread off of the table.
Turn to the right and move to the fridge.
Chill the bread in the fridge for a moment and pick it up again.
Turn around and move to the left edge of the white table.
Place the slice of bread to the right of the loaf of bread on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Chill a slice of bread and put it back on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go across the room, then turn right and go to the left end of the table across from you.
Pick up the knife, to the left of the loaf of bread, on the table.
Cut the loaf of bread on the table into slices.
Step back from the table.
Place the knife back on the table, in front of the bread.
Step back up to the table, closer to the bread.
Pick up one of the slices of bread on the table.
Turn to your right and go across the room to the refrigerator.
Place the slice of bread on the second shelf of the refrigerator, wait a moment for the bread to chill, then remove the bread from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go back to the left side of the table.
Place the slice of bread on the table, to the right of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of bread on the table.
